{"type": "article", "id": 7550, "title": "Sorapot 茶壶", "description": "", "date": "2015-03-19T08:01:32Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 15, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605234729JIeafiKYR5PjGvnA.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t美国设计师 Joey Roth 花了 4 年时间，设计出一款名为「Sorapot」的茶壶。Sorapot 运用了不锈钢与硼硅玻璃两种材质，金属部分采用旧时的熔模铸造加工工艺，最后再经过手工打磨处理，透出旧工业时代的美感。中间部位封闭的玻璃壶胆在装入散装茶叶与水后，可以通过透明的壶壁观察到茶叶在水中舒展的姿态。特别的是，Sorapot 还可以轻松一拆为二，方便用户清洗杯壁内侧的茶渍。定价 285 美元（约合人民币 1770 元），<a href=\"http://joeyroth.com/sorapot/\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234727paZzu57JVmkBDfWX.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.61333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606052347273Ui7cB0qxVZTwLnK.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.46333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234727HF3wW7CR1Tb8uYLh.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.52333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234728As3dXhMjG4WenxUL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.61333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234728JQPvutVlNzAKmkai.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.61333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}